snippet.title: Devilated - Coming October 28 to Steam and GOG
snippet.description:
Coming to Steam and GOG on October 28!

Wishlist on Steam to keep up with the launch: https://store.steampowered.com/app/570950/Devilated/
Follow us on Twitter: https://x.com/NeonDoctrine

Enter Devilated, the bastard child of an old-school shooter and action RPG after snorting a line of raw, uncut hyperviolence. Go on frantic, furiously fast and delightfully difficult romp through hell in this fever dream of chaos and carnage.
